Program: Great Lives
Title: Albert Einstein
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b007728l
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 3 Jun 2016
Time Magazine called him The Man of the Century and others have said he was 'the greatest Jew since Jesus'. His theories still make our brains spin, but what was Einstein like as a person? TV science presenter Professor Kathy Sykes discusses the archetypal crazy genius with Matthew Parris and Einstein's biographer, John Gribbin. Show less